<rss xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" version="2.0"><channel><title>NBC News Top Stories</title><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/</link><description>NBC News Top Stories</description><language>en-US</language><copyright>© 2026 NBCNews.com</copyright><lastBuildDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 05:01:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><image><url>https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/MSNBC/Components/Media/NBC-promo-graphics/nbc-news.png</url><title>NBC News Top Stories</title><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/</link></image><item><dc:creator>Phil Helsel</dc:creator><dc:creator>Mo Abbas</dc:creator><dc:creator>Daniele Hamamdjian</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Sun, 10 May 2026 05:01:11 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>The cruise ship at the center of a deadly hantavirus outbreak arrived early Sunday off the Spanish island of Tenerife, where the process of sending most passengers back to their home countries will get underway.</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/health/health-news/hantavirus-stricken-cruise-ship-arrives-tenerife-rcna344318</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/health/health-news/hantavirus-stricken-cruise-ship-arrives-tenerife-rcna344318</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260510-hondius-cc-0124a-9dc820.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1536" width="2048"><media:credit>NBC News</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Image: The MV Hondius, the ship at the center of a deadly hantavirus outbreak, arrives in Tenerife on Sunday. </media:text><media:description type="plain">The MV Hondius, the ship at the center of a deadly hantavirus outbreak, arrives in Tenerife on Sunday. After disembarking, passengers will undergo medical screenings before boarding flights that will take them back to their home countries, officials have said.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260510-hondius-cc-0124a-9dc820.jpg" height="1536" width="2048"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 05:01:11 GMT</pubDate><title>Hantavirus-stricken cruise ship arrives in Tenerife</title><updateDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 05:27:06 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Minyvonne Burke</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Sat, 09 May 2026 11:00:00 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>The recent coverage of a cruise ship hit with a deadly hantavirus outbreak is painfully familiar to cruisers who spent days and weeks trapped in their cabins at the start of the Covid-19 pandemic in 2020</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/covid-19-cruise-passengers-recall-painful-memories-hantavirus-outbreak-rcna343826</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/covid-19-cruise-passengers-recall-painful-memories-hantavirus-outbreak-rcna343826</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260508-covid-cruise-ch-1100-06bed0.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1666" width="2500"><media:credit>Jeff Greenberg</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Covid cruise.</media:text><media:description type="plain">A row of cruise ships docked in Miami in 2020 due to the coronavirus outbreak.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260503-hantavirus-cruise-safrica-ww-1855-2735c0.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>AFP via Getty Images</media:credit><media:text type="plain">A blue and white cruise ship floats in calm waters under a clear blue sky.</media:text><media:description type="plain">A row of cruise ships docked in Miami in 2020 due to the coronavirus outbreak.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260508-covid-cruise-ch-1101-7b2b0d.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Tim Rue</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Covid cruise.</media:text><media:description type="plain">A row of cruise ships docked in Miami in 2020 due to the coronavirus outbreak.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260508-covid-cruise-ch-1100-06bed0.jpg" height="1666" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate><title>Covid-19 cruise passengers recall painful memories amid hantavirus outbreak</title><updateDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 11:00:00 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Nollaig O&#39;Connor</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Sat, 09 May 2026 19:00:53 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Even after more than 100 passengers and crewmembers fell sick during a norovirus outbreak aboard the Caribbean Princess cruise ship, passenger Jan van Milligen said life on board still felt surprisingly normal.“The normal atmosphere is still here,” van Milligen, who has spent the last 21 days aboard the ship with relatives and friends from South Africa, told NBC News on Saturday.</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/world/caribbean/norovirus-outbreak-princess-cruise-caribbean-rcna344359</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/world/caribbean/norovirus-outbreak-princess-cruise-caribbean-rcna344359</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260509-Caribbean-Princess-ch-1448-8e67d8.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1666" width="2500"><media:credit>Ivan Pisarenko</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Caribbean Princess.</media:text><media:description type="plain">The outbreak sickened 102 of the ship’s 3,116 passengers and 13 crewmembers, according to the CDC.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260509-Caribbean-Princess-ch-1448-8e67d8.jpg" height="1666" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 19:00:53 GMT</pubDate><title>More than 100 sickened in norovirus outbreak aboard Caribbean Princess cruise</title><updateDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 19:00:53 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Sat, 09 May 2026 23:29:04 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>A Frontier Airlines plane aborted take off after it hit and killed a trespasser who gained access to the runway. Video from inside the plane shows panicked passengers as smoke filled the cabin. Emergency responders reported that there appeared to be “human remains on the runway.” It is unclear how the individual made it on the tarmac. NBC News’ Liz Kreutz has the latest.</description><expires>2056-05-09T23:11:01.000+0000</expires><guid isPermaLink="false">wnn_lkr_frontier_airlines_plane_hits_trespasser_260509</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/video/dramatic-video-shows-moment-frontier-airlines-flight-hits-trespasser-on-runway-263056453759</link><media:content url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/wnn_lkr_frontier_airlines_plane_hits_trespasser_260509/3/abs/index.m3u8" medium="video"><media:credit></media:credit><media:title>Dramatic video shows moment Frontier Airlines flight hits trespasser on runway</media:title><media:player url="https://www.nbcnews.com/video/dramatic-video-shows-moment-frontier-airlines-flight-hits-trespasser-on-runway-263056453759"></media:player><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1778369254449_wnn_lkr_frontier_airlines_plane_hits_trespasser_260509_S3_1920x1080-3m6r73.jpg"></media:thumbnail><media:description type="plain">A Frontier Airlines plane aborted take off after it hit and killed a trespasser who gained access to the runway. Video from inside the plane shows panicked passengers as smoke filled the cabin. Emergency responders reported that there appeared to be “human remains on the runway.” It is unclear how the individual made it on the tarmac. NBC News’ Liz Kreutz has the latest.</media:description><media:subTitle type="text/srt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1778369254449_wnn_lkr_frontier_airlines_plane_hits_trespasser_260509.srt"></media:subTitle><media:subTitle type="text/vtt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1778369254449_wnn_lkr_frontier_airlines_plane_hits_trespasser_260509.vtt"></media:subTitle></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1778369254449_wnn_lkr_frontier_airlines_plane_hits_trespasser_260509_S3_1920x1080-3m6r73.jpg"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 23:10:58 GMT</pubDate><title>Dramatic video shows moment Frontier Airlines flight hits trespasser on runway</title><updateDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 23:29:04 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Dalila Muata</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Sat, 09 May 2026 14:00:42 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Spirit Airlines was the budget-friendly carrier America loved to hate.</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/get-losers-re-buying-airline-spirit-revival-plan-going-viral-rcna343953</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/get-losers-re-buying-airline-spirit-revival-plan-going-viral-rcna343953</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260507-Spirit-Airlines-ch-1350-5f181f.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Ronaldo Silva</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Spirit Airlines,</media:text><media:descript